00:51:02.038 --> 00:51:04.124
Ms. Oh? That doesn't sound right.

00:51:05.166 --> 00:51:07.878
-What should I call you?
-What do you mean?

00:51:09.212 --> 00:51:10.171
I mean,

00:51:11.673 --> 00:51:13.216
we're now dating, so…

00:51:15.218 --> 00:51:16.303
Mr. Kang.

00:51:17.053 --> 00:51:19.681
When did we say we'd start dating?

00:51:21.141 --> 00:51:23.977
Last night, we kissed…

00:51:25.520 --> 00:51:26.855
The kiss?

00:51:26.938 --> 00:51:28.023
It's not that…

00:51:28.106 --> 00:51:33.820
People don't start dating
just because it happened once.

00:51:33.904 --> 00:51:36.448
We don't do that in this day and age.

